<blockquote>
<p>It bleeds! It breathes!</p>
<p>What stands before us, is not a machine<br />
It breathes, it will bleed and it will dream!</p>
<p>Its body is covered in hundreds of wires.<br />
and a mouth that attempts to speak, it attempts to lie<br />
